    },
    {
      "start": 145.92,
      "end": 146.9,
      "text": "They are agnostic"
    },
    {
      "start": 146.9,
      "end": 148.92,
      "text": "So whenever they get together"
    },
    {
      "start": 148.92,
      "end": 151.28,
      "text": "They're all calling him different names"
    },
    {
      "start": 151.28,
